subject: unknown male voice on cell phone
author: yramos68
full_text:
my daughter and i were making a video of us goofing around. this is a 
15 second video and we were laughing loudly. but towards the end of the 
15 seconds there we hear an unknown male voice saying "say something" 
we thought it was my brother's voice maybe perhaps coming through my 
video but then it really didnt sound truly like my brother. sounded 
more like a male voice. now what the heck was that????????? this is the 
first time this has ever happened. we are still spooked about this.

alice,
tennessee
